## Limitations

The findings are limited by the variability in study designs, sample sizes, and definitions of aggression and violence across different research. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of video games and their increasing complexity may not be fully captured in older studies. The lack of consensus in the academic community suggests that further research is needed to draw more definitive conclusions.

